  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0ddc\u0da9 \u0d9d\u0dcf\u0dad\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0da7 \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9d\u0dcf\u0dad\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Another killing for the Ambalangoda killing herd",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police Media Spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Advocate Mr. Nihal Talduwa said that a person was killed in a shooting by two people who came on a motorcycle near Balapitiya Hospital.",
        "The deceased was a 27-year-old man from Galagoda area of \u200b\u200bAmbalangoda. The media spokesperson said that it is suspected that the shootings that took place in Ambalangoda area in recent days may have been carried out by an opposing party.",
        "The spokesperson added that the shooting was done with a T56 firearm."
      ],
